value: 1611 - Highway and Street Construction, Except Elevated Highways Summary > ROADWAYS PROPRIETARY LIMITED is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover highway and street construction, except elevated highways. The company is a subsidiary of IAN HARRINGTON GROUP HOLDINGS PTY LTD. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. ROADWAYS PROPRIETARY LIMITED is headquartered in Glenorchy, Tasmania. It is headed by director & company secretary David Lindsay Wilson. For the 2023 financial year, the company reported revenue of $36.50 million. Its net profit totalled $811,000. ROADWAYS PROPRIETARY LIMITED forms part of the construction industry sector.
